			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_1 et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_1">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3  et_pb_column_1 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><img class="alignnone wp-image-2456" src="/wp-content/uploads/00IaaS.png" alt="InterVision Infrastructure as a Service IaaS" width="300" height="198" /><br />
</span></p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_3  et_pb_column_2 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h1 class="p1"><span class="s2">Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)</span></h1>
<p class="p1"><span class="s2">InterVision Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS) provides customers with the necessary compute, storage and networking for the datacenter in a hardened facility. Â It can also be viewed as an enterprise-grade data center replacement for compute and storage. Â </span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">IaaS offers resources to customers for various purposes such as Disaster Recovery, Test/Dev, New Applications and production and enables the delivery of elastic compute to address growing business needs, online storage in a variety of offerings with the necessary speed and resiliency, and carrier grade networking for servicing of applications.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s2">Infrastructure-as-a-Service provides virtual servers to organizations allowing them to start, stop, access and configure their virtual servers and storage. You pay for only as much capacity as is needed, and you can bring more storage and compute online simply as required. Â </span><span class="s1">Â You can continue to have full control of your server and its applications through our secure web portal. And we offer high-speed/low latency connection between our St. Louis and Denver data centers which allow servers to reside in both locations.</span></p>
<p class="p3"><strong><span class="s2">IaaS includes pre-sales consultation and solution design, with additional costs for implementation and ongoing support of applications with a </span><span class="s3">right-size guarantee.</span></strong></p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_2 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
