				<div class="et_pb_promo et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_cta_0" style="background-color: rgba(126,190,197,0);">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo_description">
					<h2 class="et_pb_module_header">Your server. Our datacenter.</h2>
					<p class="p4"><span class="s2">IaaS is scalable, reliable and flexible through resource sharing. Migrate your server to our secure datacenter. Gain peace of mind.</span></p>
				</div>
				<div class="et_pb_button_wrapper"><a class="et_pb_promo_button et_pb_button" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C36wxg7j5EM">See How We Do It!</a></div>
