					<h2 class="et_pb_module_header">Prepare for 2019</h2>
					<div class="row">
<div class="col">
<div id="c6633-title" class="mktoText">
<h3 class="text-center mb-4" style="text-align: center;">To help you navigate changes in the new year, InterVision has compiled a list of predictions from experts with a keen eye on the market.</h3>
</div>
</div>
</div>
