				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h1>Project Management</h1>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p>Todayâs complex IT deployments can involve dozens of stakeholders and thousands of steps. Taking action to manage risks and build contingencies to mitigate the impact can make the difference between success and failure on a project. Project management practices proven methodologies that create efficiency, improve alignment with organizational strategies, and improve outcomes.</p>
<p>The Project Management Office oversees resources, timelines and budgets are met or exceeded during project implementations and deployments. All project managers are PMP-certified.</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3  et_pb_column_2 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_cta_0" style="background-color: #8600f4;">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo_description">
					<h2 class="et_pb_module_header">Project Management Services Overview</h2>
					
				</div>
				<div class="et_pb_button_wrapper"><a class="et_pb_promo_button et_pb_button" href="/wp-content/uploads/IV-Services-Overview-PM.pdf">Download now</a></div>
			</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_2">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2  et_pb_column_3 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_2">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h2>Why partner with InterVision?</h2>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_3">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p>InterVision Project Managers can design a deployment plan according to your needs, handling the full implementation. Issues that arise are addressed in a timely and efficient manner, keeping your implementation on schedule. If your needs change over the course of a project, our project managers will work with you to ensure that those changes are properly captured and communicated to the rest of the project team. InterVision Project Management services can help you:</p>
<ul>
<li>Clarify expectations</li>
<li>Avoid service cost over runs and schedule misses</li>
<li>Increase the flow of communication between all stakeholders</li>
<li>Mitigate risk</li>
<li>Improve the chances of a successful implementation</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2  et_pb_column_4 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_4">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h2>Project Management Deliverables</h2>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_5">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<ul>
<li>Task breakdown with milestones</li>
<li>Detailed Project Gantt chart</li>
<li>Single point of contact for all IV Implementation Services</li>
<li>Weekly status meeting via phone or on site based on customer desire</li>
<li>Ongoing Risk Analysis and Mitigation strategy</li>
<li>Communication Plan</li>
<li>Detailed progress reporting</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_2 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_3">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_5 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_text_align_left ntl-scale-down et_pb_cta_1" style="background-color: rgba(126,190,197,0);">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo_description">
					<h2 class="et_pb_module_header">World-Class Local Expertise</h2>
					<p>Next generation, IT professionals making your business, their business. Our goal is to unlock value on your way to success.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="et_pb_button_wrapper"><a class="et_pb_promo_button et_pb_button" href="/wp-content/uploads/IV-ProServe_Overview.pdf">Get the Overview</a></div>
