				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_1 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et-waypoint et_animated et_pb_image_0 et_always_center_on_mobile">
				
				
				<a href="https://www.cohesity.com/"><span class="et_pb_image_wrap"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/Cohesity-logo.png" alt="Cohesity" /></span></a>
			</div><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p>Remaking Secondary Storage</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h3 class="p1">Consolidate all secondary data and associated mangement functions into one unified solution.</h3>
<hr />
<p>Cohesity makes large organizations productive by consolidating, protecting and sharing your non-mission-critical data assets. Your essential data is instantly available when you need it, where you need it.</p>
<p>Their ground-breaking distributed systems technology hyperconverges all secondary storage workloads into an efficient, agile and infinitely scalable resource pool. This greatly simplifies both your infrastructure and the resources to administer it.</p>
<p align="left">Traditional secondary storage isÂ fragmented and inefficient, consuming aboutÂ 80%Â of enterprise storage capacity as data is copied on average 10 to 12 times across individual storage appliances in support of different use cases like backup, analytics, test/dev, files and objects. To move data to the public cloud, organizations have to deploy yet another silo in the form of a cloud gateway.</p>
<p align="left">CohesityÂ transforms this complex infrastructure with aÂ simple, elegant solution. Cohesity DataPlatform eliminates secondary storage silosÂ with a single, purpose-built hyperconverged platform. The Cohesity solution enables organizations toÂ cut their total cost of ownership by 80%Â or more compared to traditional solutions.Â DataPlatform provides distributed storage with best-in-class space efficiency, efficient copy data management, and native cloud integration. The platform incorporates data management functions for converged data protection, in-place analytics, and copy data management to automate DevOps workflows.</p>
<p class="p4"><strong><span class="s2">Find out more at <a href="http://www.cohesity.com/"><span class="s4">www.cohesity.com</span></a></span></strong></p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_2 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
