			</div><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p>A short path to better software</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h3 class="p1">Â Automatically deliver and operate all of your software across its entire lifecycle.</h3>
<div class="body">
<p>Today, software is everywhere. Itâs on our wrists, on our walls, and in our cars. Itâs changed the way we shop, the way we work, the way we heal, and the way we stay connected to those we love.</p>
<p>Yet we also know there is no future with fewer servers. Software is only getting more complex, evolving faster than humans can keep pace. How can we benefit from future innovation if it takes too long or costs too much to implement it?</p>
<p>Itâs time to fundamentally improve the way we do things so we can change without constraint.</p>
<p>PuppetÂ is leading the movement that will define the next decade of software.</p>
<p>Today itâs characterized by the general realization that for companies to remain relevant, they have to constantly provide great software to their users. Tomorrow itâs defined by a world of frictionless software change â where any company can deliver a better experience to their users, at any moment.</p>
<p>Puppet is building a world of unconstrained software change. Where the software that powers everything around us is always available, is constantly modern, and accessible from anywhere.</p>
</div>
<p class="p4"><strong><span class="s2">Find out more at</span><span class="s2"> <a href="https://puppet.com/"><span class="s4">www.puppet.com</span></a></span></strong></p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
