				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p style="text-align: center;">Client Service Management provides tightly-bound service personnel, trained and capable of providing ongoing consultation, change management and support above and beyond NetTend. These designated experts augment the Hosted Cafe team to provide tight alignment with your business initiatives as determined by a mutually defined service management plan.</p>
