					<h3 class="p1">Progress lives at the intersection of technology and humanity.</h3>
<hr />
<p>Our connected world is undergoing its latest digital transformationâchanging industries and creating fundamental shifts in the way we work and live.</p>
<p>To shape this brighter future, DELL EMC is bringing together the industryâs best technologies to empower the next generation of business leaders, doctors, teachers, engineers, entrepreneurs and everyone in between. No matter the use case or business demands, their data storage systems help you do more, move faster, and perform better.</p>
<p>Dell EMC serves a key role in providing the essential infrastructure for organizations to build their digital future, transform IT and protect their most important asset, information. Dell EMC enablesÂ  customersâ IT and digital business transformation through trusted hybrid cloud and big-data solutions, built upon a modern data center infrastructure that incorporates industry-leading converged infrastructure, servers, and storage. Dell EMC brings together Dellâs and EMCâs respective strong capabilities, complementary portfolios and R&amp;D; providing capabilities spanning strategy development, consultative services, solution deployment helping customers and partners drive the digital transformation of their businesses.</p>
<p><strong>Find out more at <a href="https://www.dellemc.com/en-us/index.htm">www.dellemc.com</a></strong></p>
