							<article id="post-2875" class="cf singular post-2875 page type-page status-publish hentry" role="article" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">

								<section class="entry-content cf" itemprop="articleBody">
									<div class="at-above-post-page addthis_tool" data-url="https://www.intervision.com/intervision-technologies/att/"></div><div class="et_builder_outer_content" id="et_builder_outer_content">
				<div class="et_builder_inner_content et_pb_gutters3">
					<div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_0 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_0">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_0 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_slider et_pb_slider_fullwidth_off et_slider_auto et_slider_speed_8000  et_pb_slider_0">
				<div class="et_pb_slides">
					 <div class="et_pb_slide et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_media_alignment_center et_pb_slide_0 et-pb-active-slide">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_container clearfix">
					<div class="et_pb_slider_container_inner">
						
						<div class="et_pb_slide_description">
							<h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">AT&amp;T</h2>
							<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><p>AT&amp;T Partner Exchange Services provide speed, reliability and mobility when it counts most.</p></div>
							
						</div> <!-- .et_pb_slide_description -->
					</div>
				</div> <!-- .et_pb_container -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_slide -->
			 
				</div> <!-- .et_pb_slides -->
				<style>.et_pb_slider_0.et_pb_slider .et_pb_slide {-webkit-box-shadow: none; -moz-box-shadow: none; box-shadow: none; }</style>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_slider -->
			
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_1 et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_1">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_1 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_image et-waypoint et_animated et_pb_image_0 et_always_center_on_mobile">
				
				
				<a href="https://www.att.com/" target="_blank"><span class="et_pb_image_wrap"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/apex_sp-badge_plat-elite_horz_rgb_pos-e1490046859661.png" alt="" title="AT&amp;T Partner Exchange" /></span></a>
			</div><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					 AT&amp;T Partner Exchange Services 
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p>AT&amp;T is a leading provider of wireless, Wi-Fi, high speed Internet, voice and cloud-based network services. As a Platinum Elite Solution Provider in the AT&amp;T Partner Exchange, InterVision offers a diverse array of services and solutions in the areas of network, cloud, hosting and enterprise mobility with specialization in AVPN.</p>
<h2>AT&amp;T Virtual Private Network</h2>
<p>An Internet Protocol (IP) VPN provides the foundation that connects the main office, data centers, branch offices, and remote and mobile workers to each other, and to the applications they need to be productive.</p>
<p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Quickly scale AT&amp;T VPN to satisfy business growth or merger integration.</li>
<li>Easily deploy business continuity options using remote access and mobile Internet.</li>
<li>Extend the VPN to mobile devices, so they are simply an additional endpoint on the network.</li>
<li>Get consistent performance across locations and devices.</li>
<li>Select how much management the business needs by using flexible management options.</li>
</ul>
<h2>AT&amp;T Managed Internet Service</h2>
<p>More than just an Internet connection, AT&amp;T Managed Internet Service is a complete access and technical solution. AT&amp;T Managed Internet Service provides a dedicated Internet connection with extensive reach throughout the United States (including Puerto Rico and U.S. Virgin Islands). AT&amp;T proactively monitors Internet access around the clock, and provides enhanced features to help protect critical business applications.</p>
<p><strong>BENEFITS</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Connection to the Internet is dedicated, not shared with other businesses.</li>
<li>Backed by industry-leading service level agreements that provide 100% service availability.</li>
<li>Offers a wide range of access speeds, billing plans, and bundled options like Voice over IP service</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_2 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_2">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_2 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_cta_0" style="background-color: rgba(126,190,197,0);">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_promo_description">
					<h2 class="et_pb_module_header">Authentication and access control</h2>
					<p class="p2"><span class="s2">Itâs vital to your security posture to have a solid understanding of who is accessing what in your environment. Gain peace of mind by peeling back the layers and developing a solid plan. </span></p>
<p><!--HubSpot Call-to-Action Code --><br />
<span id="hs-cta-wrapper-537bda30-8841-4271-9551-421e69c73d5c" class="hs-cta-wrapper"><br />
