				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h2>Why partner with InterVision?</h2>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_3">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<ul>
<li>InterVisionâs storage team is well qualified to help you <strong>analyze your growing storage environment</strong> and <strong>make recommendations to optimize your storage</strong>. InterVision has:
<ul>
<li>Designing and installing more than 1,000 complex enterprise storage installations</li>
<li>Over 100 Storage Assessments completed to date</li>
<li>NetApp Star Partner and NetApp Authorized Service Provider</li>
<li>Close ties to NetApp include executive-level relationships</li>
<li>FlexPod Premium Partner</li>
<li>FlexPod and NetApp equipment in our Technology Lab.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_4">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h2>Benefits of a NetApp Storage Assessment</h2>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_5">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<ul>
<li>Identify ideas to support your business environment</li>
<li>Identify cost saving measures and consolidation opportunities</li>
<li>Identify strengths, weaknesses and opportunities for improvement</li>
<li>Gain information to help you create plans to scale your infrastructure</li>
<li>Collect detailed information on the applications and systems in place</li>
<li>Gain insights into the performance and resiliency of your entire storage infrastructure</li>
<li>Provide a detailed recommendations on how to improve and optimize your overall storage environment in the most cost effective manner</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2  et_pb_column_4 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
