					<h2>NetApp Storage Assessment Deliverables</h2>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_7">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<ul>
<li>Once the assessment is complete, you will have the information needed to make informed decisions regarding your storage environment. The deliverables include a report detailing the following:
<ul>
<li>Usage trends data and patterns</li>
<li>Performance analysis with performance capacity and best practices</li>
<li>Volume capacity forecasting</li>
<li>LUN alignment</li>
<li>Wiring diagram</li>
<li>Recommendations on optimizing your environment</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
