					<p>Open technology for the cloud</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h3 class="p1"><span class="s2">With an open hybrid cloud infrastructure from Red Hat, your IT organization can better serve your business by delivering more agile and flexible solutions while protecting business assets and preparing for the future.</span></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>More than 2 decades ago, Red Hat had a spark of an ideaâa vision for developing software differently. We believed that collaboration with an ecosystem of IT leaders, open source advocates, developers, and partners could create a better foundation for the future of ITâRed Hat<sup>Â®</sup>Â Enterprise Linux<sup>Â®</sup>.</p>
<p class="p4"><span class="s2">Since inception, Red Hat has been helping customers navigate technology and business disruption through open innovation.Â Open source communities are solving some of the most complex business and IT challenges today. The freedom to see the code, ask questions, and offer improvements back to the community: this is the open source way.</span></p>
<p class="p4"><span class="s2">Red Hat connects an innovative community of customers, partners, and contributors to deliver an open source stack of trusted, high-performing technologies that solve business problems. They areÂ a billion dollar S&amp;P 500 company offering solutions from Linux to middleware, storage to cloud,</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="p4"><strong><span class="s2">Find out more at <a href="https://www.redhat.com/en"><span class="s4">www.redhat.com</span></a></span></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
