				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h1>The IT Operations Workshop helps IT staff evaluate and prioritize their IT services and delivery model to improve operational maturity and enable business differentiation.</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>InterVision facilitates a collaborativeÂ workshop to bringÂ company&#8217;s key IT stakeholders and subject matter experts together to <strong>better understand their capabilities, resourcing approach and operational gaps</strong> by leveraging InterVision&#8217;s expertise to <strong>develop solutions</strong> that map directly to <strong>operational improvements that deliver business value</strong>.</p>
<p>Involving key stakeholders at the director-level, this five-hour session with some pre-work, results in a presentation that includes recommendations for IT operational enhancements and a InterVision managed solution aimed at improving the overall operational maturity level.</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_promo et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_text_align_center  et_pb_cta_0" style="background-color: #0c71c3;">
				
				
