				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<img class="aligncenter wp-image-3442" src="/wp-content/uploads/reduce-costs.png" alt="" width="125" height="125" srcset="https://www.intervision.com/wp-content/uploads/reduce-costs.png 252w, https://www.intervision.com/wp-content/uploads/reduce-costs-125x125.png 125w" sizes="(max-width: 125px) 100vw, 125px" />
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Reduces Costs</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">as a service model, NetDefend reduces significant initial investment, cost of internal staffing for security and compliance specialists.</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4  et_pb_column_4 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center  et_pb_text_3">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h3 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-3441" src="/wp-content/uploads/simplify.png" alt="" width="125" height="125" srcset="https://www.intervision.com/wp-content/uploads/simplify.png 252w, https://www.intervision.com/wp-content/uploads/simplify-125x125.png 125w" sizes="(max-width: 125px) 100vw, 125px" />Simplifies security management</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">by providing security infrastructure admin and management with best in class tools and processes.</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4  et_pb_column_5 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
