								<section class="entry-content cf" itemprop="articleBody">
									<div class="at-above-post-page addthis_tool" data-url="https://www.intervision.com/solutions-services/on-premises/storage/"></div><div class="et_builder_outer_content" id="et_builder_outer_content">
				<div class="et_builder_inner_content et_pb_gutters3">
					<div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_0 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular et_section_transparent">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_0">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_0 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_slider et_pb_slider_fullwidth_off et_slider_auto et_slider_speed_8000  et_pb_slider_0">
				<div class="et_pb_slides">
					 <div class="et_pb_slide et_pb_bg_layout_dark et_pb_media_alignment_center et_pb_slide_0 et-pb-active-slide">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_container clearfix">
					<div class="et_pb_slider_container_inner">
						
						<div class="et_pb_slide_description">
							<h2 class="et_pb_slide_title">Technologies</h2>
							<div class="et_pb_slide_content"><p>/Â <span class="s1">Storage</span></p></div>
							
						</div> <!-- .et_pb_slide_description -->
					</div>
				</div> <!-- .et_pb_container -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_slide -->
			 
				</div> <!-- .et_pb_slides -->
				<style>.et_pb_slider_0.et_pb_slider .et_pb_slide {-webkit-box-shadow: none; -moz-box-shadow: none; box-shadow: none; }</style>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_slider -->
			
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row -->
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_section --><div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_1 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular">
				
				
				
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_1">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_1 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column ntl-scale-down et_pb_text_0">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Storage</span></p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left ntl-full-column et_pb_text_1">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<p class="p1" style="text-align: left;">The question remains: <strong>On-premises storage or cloud?</strong><br />
It is conversation we have every day with our customers as we guide them through data center strategy discussions.</p>
<p class="p1" style="text-align: left;">The good news? Netelligent can do it all regardless ofÂ the size of your organization or how diverse your data.</p>
<p class="p1" style="text-align: left;"><strong>On-Premises</strong><br />
InterVision has partnered with the leaders in storage technology to deliver the best possible experience for our customers. InterVision partners with Cisco, NetApp, Hitachi Data Systems, IBM, Dell, Hewlett-Packard to address any workload for any customer.</p>
<p><strong>Hybrid IT Solution</strong><br />
Not ready or unable to fully commit to cloud storage? No problem. We have many customers that have a variety requirements. On premise with managed services? No problem. On premise with Disaster recovery as a Service and backup to an InterVision Data Center? Sounds good. InterVision can meet you exactly where you are in your cloud journey, develop a plan, and deliver results.<br />
<strong><br />
Cloud</strong><br />
Ready to move everything to the cloud? With a strict SLA delivering best in class performance and availability, the Hosted CafÃ© cloud option for storage is a great option. Trying to figure out another cloud vendorâs portal, cost structure, and migration plan? Leave the heavy lifting to InterVision. Our team of engineers can deliver a full solution including migration services, storage, security, and data recovery solution.</p>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4  et_pb_column_2 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_space et_pb_divider_hidden et_pb_divider_0"><div class="et_pb_divider_internal"></div></div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_2">
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2  et_pb_column_3 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_2">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h2>Benefits of Using a Storage Methodology</h2>
<ul>
<li>Simplify storage management and lower administration costs</li>
<li>Maximize your current storage investment</li>
<li>Reduce the waste of underutilized storage assets</li>
<li>Provide greater scalability for future growth</li>
<li>Create a storage optimization strategy that aligns with your business needs</li>
<li>Ensure compliance</li>
<li>Lower long-term storage costs</li>
<li>Meet your backup, archival and disaster recovery requirements</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2  et_pb_column_4 et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_3">
				
				
				<div class="et_pb_text_inner">
					<h2>Why InterVision?</h2>
<ul>
<li>InterVision can help you navigate the complexities of storage, and help you design and implement a storage architecture that meets your unique requirements. Our engineering staff has specific expertise around storage solutions. InterVision has:
<ul>
<li>Designed and installed more than 1,000 complex enterprise storage installations</li>
<li>Long-term relationships with the leading storage vendors in network attached storage, storage area networks, and direct attached storage</li>
<li>Top certifications from leading storage vendors, including NetApp, Hitachi Data Systems, IBM, Dell, Hewlett-Packard</li>
<li>Relationships with emerging storage vendors on the latest SSD storage solutions</li>
<li>Expertise in storage virtualization</li>
<li>Access to converged infrastructure stacks from HDS, FlexPod, and HP in our Technology Lab.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
				</div>
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
				
				
